== 宣傳及發行 ==
=== 宣傳 ===
2015年6月11日，[[華特迪士尼動畫工作室|華特迪士尼動畫工作室]]於[[YouTube|YouTube]]上發布了《動物方城市》的第一部前導預告片<ref>{{en}}[[華特迪士尼動畫工作室|Walt Disney Animation Studio]], [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g9lmhBYB11U "Zootopia US Teaser Trailer"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g9lmhBYB11U |date=20150618184345 }}</ref>，而這部預告片也同時在電影院中[[皮克斯|皮克斯]]的動畫電影《[[腦筋急轉彎_(電影)|腦筋急轉彎]]》播映前放映。第二部前導預告片於同年11月23日同樣在YouTube上發布（並在電影院中《[[恐龍當家|恐龍當家]]》播映前放映）<ref>{{en}}[[華特迪士尼動畫工作室|Walt Disney Animation Studio]], [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bY73vFGhSVk "Zootopia Official US Sloth Trailer"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bY73vFGhSVk |date=20151124023508 }}</ref>，其中包含了主角茱蒂和尼克在哺乳動物車輛管理局中向[[樹懶|樹懶]][[公務員|公務員]]尋求幫助的橋段。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/zootopia-trailer-dmv-sloths-1201646717/|last=McNary|first=Dave|title='Zootopia' Trailer Proves That Sloths Run the DMV|publisher=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]|date=2015-11-23|accessdate=2016-06-29|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160703033249/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/zootopia-trailer-dmv-sloths-1201646717/|archivedate=2016-07-03}}</ref>而官方的劇場版預告片則是於2015年12月31日在YouTube上發布，片中的背景音樂首次使用了[[夏奇拉|夏奇拉]]所演唱的主題曲《[[嘗試一切|嘗試一切]]》。<ref>{{en}}[[華特迪士尼動畫工作室|Walt Disney Animation Studio]], [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jWM0ct-OLsM "Zootopia Official US Trailer #2"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jWM0ct-OLsM |date=20151231170633 }}</ref>在電影於北美地區上映前的2016年2月27日至2月28日，《動物方城市》在[[美國|美國]][[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]][[華特迪士尼世界度假區|華特迪士尼世界度假區]]的[[迪士尼之泉|迪士尼之泉]]舉行了試映會，並邀請了約400位迪士尼樂園官方部落格的讀者參加。<ref>{{en}}{{Cite web|url=https://disneyparks.disney.go.com/blog/2016/03/disney-parks-blog-readers-applaud-zootopia-at-meet-up/|title=Disney Parks Blog Readers Applaud 'Zootopia' At Meet-Up|accessdate=2016-06-30|author=|date=2016-03-02|last=Fickley-Baker|first=Jennifer|publisher=Disney Parks Blog|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160819074628/https://disneyparks.disney.go.com/blog/2016/03/disney-parks-blog-readers-applaud-zootopia-at-meet-up/|archivedate=2016-08-19}}</ref>

此外，迪士尼曾和一家名叫聯盟整合媒體（Allied Integrated Media）的[[數位行銷|數位行銷]]公司簽約，由該公司在{{tsl|en|Meetup (website)|Meetup}}網站上向[[獸迷|獸迷]]族群進行宣傳，鼓勵他們將自己穿著[[兽装|獸裝]]的照片發布至[[社群網站|社群網站]]上並加上這部電影的[[主題標籤|主題標籤]]，以作為一種[[病毒式行銷|病毒式行銷]]的手法。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|last1=Notopoulos|first1=Katie|title=Proof Disney Is Actually Marketing "Zootopia" To Furries|url=http://www.buzzfeed.com/katienotopoulos/proof-disney-is-actually-marketing-zootopia-to-furries#.fw13YbMro|website=[[BuzzFeed|BuzzFeed]]|publisher=BuzzFeed, Inc|accessdate=2016-03-04|date=2016-03-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303121845/http://www.buzzfeed.com/katienotopoulos/proof-disney-is-actually-marketing-zootopia-to-furries#.fw13YbMro|archivedate=2016-03-03|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web|last1=Grauso|first1=Alisha|title=In Hindsight: How The Marketing Of 'Zootopia' Won Big By Getting Weird|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/alishagrauso/2016/03/07/in-hindsight-how-the-marketing-of-zootopia-won-big-by-getting-weird/|website=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|publisher=Forbes.com LLC|accessdate=2016-03-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160315015543/http://www.forbes.com/sites/alishagrauso/2016/03/07/in-hindsight-how-the-marketing-of-zootopia-won-big-by-getting-weird/|archivedate=2016-03-15|date=2016-03-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>此外，迪士尼也和{{tsl|en|transportation network company|交通網路公司}}[[優步|優步]]合作；在上映日2016年3月4日當天，使用者若在優步的應用程式中輸入促銷代碼「ZUBER」，地圖上[[計程車|計程車]]的圖示即會變為電影中動物汽車的模樣。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=https://newsroom.uber.com/zootopia/|author=Sarah|title=Zootopia: Your Zuber is Arriving Now!|publisher=[[優步|Uber]]|date=2016-03-03|accessdate=2016-06-29|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818124614/https://newsroom.uber.com/zootopia/|archivedate=2016-08-18}}</ref>

=== 上映 ===
《動物方城市》於2016年3月4日在[[北美地区|北美地區]]以2D、[[3D電影|迪士尼數位3D]]、[[RealD_戲院|RealD 3D]]和[[IMAX#IMAX_3D|IMAX 3D]]等形式正式上映<ref name="zoo"/><ref name="nasdaq1"/>，而這部電影是迪士尼繼2002年的《[[星银岛|星銀島]]》以後第一部在美國國內[[IMAX|IMAX]]戲院上映的動畫電影。在[[英國|英國]]等部分[[歐洲|歐洲]]國家上映時，電影原文名稱並未使用北美地區的「''Zootopia''」而改採「''Zootropolis''」，劇情中出現相應台詞的配音也有被重新修改；前者意義上是由[[動物園|動物園]]（zoo）和[[烏托邦|烏托邦]]（utopia）兩字組成，而後者則是由動物園和[[大都市|大都市]]（metropolis）兩字組成。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.screendaily.com/news/disneys-zootopia-renamed-zootropolis-for-uk/5084129.article|title=Disney's 'Zootopia' renamed 'Zootropolis' for UK|last=Rosser|first=Stephen|date=2015-03-11|work=ScreenDaily|publisher={{tsl|en|Screen International}}|accessdate=2015-03-11|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150312012104/http://www.screendaily.com/news/disneys-zootopia-renamed-zootropolis-for-uk/5084129.article|archivedate=2015-03-12}}</ref><ref name="empire">{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=43677|title=Disney's Zootopia Is Now Zootropolis|last=White|first=James|date=2015-03-11|work=[[帝國雜誌|Empire]]|publisher={{tsl|en|Bauer Media Group}}|accessdate=2015-03-11|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402171611/http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=43677|archivedate=2015-04-02}}</ref><ref name="SI">{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.screendaily.com/news/disneys-zootopia-renamed-zootropolis-for-uk/5084129.article|title=Disney's 'Zootopia' renamed 'Zootropolis' for UK|last=Rosser|first=Stephen|work=ScreenDaily|publisher={{tsl|en|Screen International}}|date=2015-03-11|accessdate=2015-03-11|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150312012104/http://www.screendaily.com/news/disneys-zootopia-renamed-zootropolis-for-uk/5084129.article|archivedate=2015-03-12}}</ref><ref name="empire"/>此外，[[德國|德國]]地區的片名則是「''Zoomania''」。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |last=Hoffman |first=Jordan |date=2016-03-03 |title=Zootopia review – Disney's furry fable gets its claws out for the bigots |url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2016/mar/03/zootopia-zootropolis-zoomania-review-disney |newspaper=[[衛報|The Guardian]] |access-date=2016-03-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160328104820/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2016/mar/03/zootopia-zootropolis-zoomania-review-disney |archivedate=2016-03-28 }}</ref><ref name="PRC">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/robcain/2016/03/08/zootopia-stampedes-across-china-to-record-box-office-results/|title='Zootopia' Stampedes Across China to Record Box Office Results|accessdate=2016-03-09|date=2016-03-08|last=Cain|first=Rob|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308195407/http://www.forbes.com/sites/robcain/2016/03/08/zootopia-stampedes-across-china-to-record-box-office-results/|archivedate=2016-03-08}}</ref>迪士尼表示這些更改「只是為了讓英國的觀眾們能有一個對他們來說更為適切的片名」<ref name="SI"/>，但《[[衛報|衛報]]》和《[[愛爾蘭時報|愛爾蘭時報]]》等媒體則指出這是為了避免在宣傳和銷售時與當地已存在的商品或地名發生名稱相同的法律糾紛<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|title=Case details for trade mark EU008214249|url=https://www.ipo.gov.uk/tmcase/Results/4/EU008214249|website={{tsl|en|Intellectual Property Office (United Kingdom)|Intellectual Property Office}}|accessdate=2016-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160813124319/https://www.ipo.gov.uk/tmcase/Results/4/EU008214249|archive-date=2016-08-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>；舉例而言，[[丹麥|丹麥]]的{{tsl|da|Givskud Zoo|吉夫斯庫動物園}}將在2019年新增一個名叫「Zootopia」的園區、而英國也曾有一張相同名稱的[[兒歌|兒歌]]專輯。<ref>{{en}}{{Cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/ie/album/zootopia/id346039735|title=Zootopia by Sally Stapleton on Apple Music|accessdate=2016-07-21|publisher=[[Apple_Music|Apple Music]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160918202923/https://itunes.apple.com/ie/album/zootopia/id346039735|archivedate=2016-09-18}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news|last1=Lee|first1=Benjamin|title=Zootopia (aka Zootropolis). Why are film titles still being changed for international release?|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/filmblog/2016/mar/09/why-are-film-titles-still-being-changed-for-international-release|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2016-03-09|accessdate=2016-06-25|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170417034925/https://www.theguardian.com/film/filmblog/2016/mar/09/why-are-film-titles-still-being-changed-for-international-release|archivedate=2017-04-17}}</ref><ref name="Why is Zootopia called Zootropolis here? And why is Disney being so coy about explaining the change?">{{en}}{{cite news|last1=Clarke|first1=Donald|title=Why is Zootopia called Zootropolis here? And why is Disney being so coy about explaining the change?|url=http://www.irishtimes.com/blogs/screenwriter/2016/03/10/why-is-zootopia-called-zootropolis-here/|newspaper=[[愛爾蘭時報|The Irish Times]]|accessdate=2016-03-24|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160329051301/http://www.irishtimes.com/blogs/screenwriter/2016/03/10/why-is-zootopia-called-zootropolis-here/|archivedate=2016-03-29}}</ref>

此外，電影中角色ZNN新聞台主播的物種在各地上映時並不相同；[[日本|日本]]的日語版本是一隻[[狸貓|狸貓]]、[[澳大利亚|澳大利亞]]及[[新西兰|紐西蘭]]的版本是一隻[[無尾熊|無尾熊]]、[[中國大陸|中國大陸]]的版本是一隻[[大熊猫|大熊貓]]、[[巴西|巴西]]及[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]的葡萄牙語版本是一隻[[美洲豹|美洲豹]]、包含北美在內的其餘國家和地區的英語版本（澳大利亞、紐西蘭除外），以及除上述國家及地區外的非英語版本則是一隻[[駝鹿|駝鹿]]。<ref name="ct">{{zh-hant}}{{cite web|url=http://photo.chinatimes.com/20160309003700-260806|title=《動物方城市》竟藏了這麼多細節！21個有趣內幕|accessdate=|date=2016-03-09|author=羅依柔|publisher=[[中國時報|中國時報]]|language=|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160313044827/http://photo.chinatimes.com/20160309003700-260806|archivedate=2016-03-13}}</ref><ref name="anchor">{{en}}{{Cite web|url=http://mentalfloss.com/article/76784/zootopia-has-different-news-anchors-different-countries|title='Zootopia' Has Different News Anchors for Different Countries|accessdate=2016-07-02|date=2016-03-08|last=O'Connell|first=Rebecca|publisher={{tsl|en|Mental Floss|Mental Floss}}|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160620015308/http://mentalfloss.com/article/76784/zootopia-has-different-news-anchors-different-countries|archivedate=2016-06-20}}</ref>而根據各地區的[[電影分級制度|電影分級制度]]，該片在美國分為PG級、[[香港電影分級制度|香港]]分為I級、台灣分為普遍級。<ref>{{en}}{{Cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2948356/parentalguide|title=Parents Guide for Zootopia (2016)|accessdate=2016-07-03|publisher=[[IMDb|IMDb]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160801142737/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2948356/parentalguide|archivedate=2016-08-01}}</ref>

本片在中國大陸上映後，曾一度掀起飼養[[耳廓狐|耳廓狐]]的熱潮<ref>{{zh-hant}}{{Cite news|url=http://www.ettoday.net/news/20160318/665126.htm|title=這不是週邊！《方城市》耳廓狐太紅　網賣活體一隻20萬|date=2016-03-18|work=[[ETtoday_東森新聞雲|ETtoday 東森新聞雲]]|accessdate=2016-07-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630214546/http://www.ettoday.net/news/20160318/665126.htm|archivedate=2016-06-30}}</ref>。然而值得一提的是，耳廓狐已在2015年被[[國際自然保護聯盟|國際自然保護聯盟]]列入[[國際自然保護聯盟瀕危物種紅色名錄|瀕危物種紅色名錄]]，任何人私自買賣均屬違法。<ref>{{zh-hant}}{{cite news|url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20160316/54873320/|title=《優獸大都會》掀養狐熱潮 瀕危耳廓狐網標3萬2隻|date=2016-03-16|publisher=[[香港蘋果日報|香港蘋果日報]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160416170659/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20160316/54873320/|archivedate=2016-04-16|accessdate=2016-04-05}}</ref>

