== 反響 ==
=== 票房 ===
{{Asof|2016|8|4|df=US}}，《動物方城市》在[[北美地区|北美地區]]的票房總額為3.41億美元，在世界其他國家和地區票房總額為6.82億美元，全球票房達10.24億美元，超過1.5億美元的總預算<ref name="budget"/><ref name="BOM" />，成為所有原創電影（非續集或改編自其它作品）中總票房收入第二高的電影（僅次於《[[阿凡達|阿凡達]]》）<ref name="Leggy">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/05/30/box-office-disneys-zootopia-tops-lion-king-to-become-second-biggest-original-movie-ever/#738afeb29ac6|title=Box Office: Disney's 'Zootopia' Is Now The Second-Biggest Original Movie Ever|accessdate=2016-05-30|author=Scott Mendelson|date=2016-05-30|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160530233716/http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/05/30/box-office-disneys-zootopia-tops-lion-king-to-become-second-biggest-original-movie-ever/#738afeb29ac6|archivedate=2016-05-30}}</ref>。在電影上映後第二週的2016年3月18日，《動物方城市》成為繼《[[冰雪奇緣|冰雪奇緣]]》和《[[超能陸戰隊|大英雄天團]]》後，[[華特迪士尼動畫工作室|迪士尼]]連續第三部全球票房突破5億美元的動畫電影。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/zootopia-to-cross-500m-globally-today-1201722585/|title='Zootopia' To Cross $500M Globally Today|accessdate=2016-03-19|author=Anita Busch|date=2016-03-18|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160320152331/http://deadline.com/2016/03/zootopia-to-cross-500m-globally-today-1201722585/|archivedate=2016-03-20}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/03/18/box-office-disneys-zootopia-tops-500m-worldwide/#1800ef3b3002|title=Box Office: Disney's 'Zootopia' Tops $500M Worldwide|accessdate=2016-03-19|author=Scott Mendelson|date=2016-03-18|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319050303/http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/03/18/box-office-disneys-zootopia-tops-500m-worldwide/#1800ef3b3002|archivedate=2016-03-19}}</ref>接著，它的全球票房收入分別在同年的4月5日及4月24日突破8億和9億美元的關卡<ref name="Overseas19thOpening">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/04/the-jungle-book-huntsman-winters-war-zootopia-batman-superman-international-box-office-weekend-results-1201742754/|title='Jungle Book' A $337M Offshore Beast As 'Huntsman' Musters $80M; 'Zootopia' Tops $900M Global – Intl B.O. Update|accessdate=2016-04-25|author=Nancy Tartaglione|date=2016-04-24|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160424223707/http://deadline.com/2016/04/the-jungle-book-huntsman-winters-war-zootopia-batman-superman-international-box-office-weekend-results-1201742754/|archivedate=2016-04-24}}</ref><ref name="Toon">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/04/zootopia-crosses-800-million-worldwide-box-office-1201732382/|title='Zootopia' Hops To $800M+ Global; Top 2016 Grosser Still Has Play To Come|accessdate=2016-04-06|author=Nancy Tartaglione and Anita Busch|date=2016-04-05|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160406114545/http://deadline.com/2016/04/zootopia-crosses-800-million-worldwide-box-office-1201732382/|archivedate=2016-04-06}}</ref>，並於6月5日成為2016年第二部全球票房達到10億美元的電影（繼《[[美國隊長3：英雄內戰|美國隊長3：英雄內戰]]》之後）<ref name="1billion">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/06/zootopia-passes-one-billion-worldwide-box-office-disney-1201767542/|title='Zootopia' Hops Past $1B Global Box Office; Disney's 11th Time Over The Mark|accessdate=2016-06-05|author=Nancy Tartaglione|date=2016-06-05|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160605221552/http://deadline.com/2016/06/zootopia-passes-one-billion-worldwide-box-office-disney-1201767542/|archivedate=2016-06-05}}</ref>；這也是迪士尼第三部、及有史以來第四部實現此票房-{里}-程碑的動畫電影。<ref name=":2">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=worldwide&yr=2016|title=2016 WORLDWIDE GROSSES|accessdate=2016-04-03|work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160402133629/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=worldwide&yr=2016|archivedate=2016-04-02}}</ref><ref name=":3">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/genres/chart/?id=animation.htm|title=Animation|accessdate=2016-04-03|work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160819221907/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/genres/chart/?id=animation.htm|archivedate=2016-08-19}}</ref>最後，《動物方城市》成為當時迪士尼全球票房收入第二高的動畫電影（僅次於《[[冰雪奇緣|冰雪奇緣]]》）<ref name="Toon" />，以及[[2016年電影列表|2016年全球總票房收入第四高的電影]]，同時也是有史以來[[最高電影票房收入列表|全球票房收入第37名的電影]]。<ref name=":1" />

==== 北美地區 ====
《動物方城市》在[[美國|美國]]和[[加拿大|加拿大]]地區共3827間電影院上映前，其首週末的預測票房收入為6000萬至7000萬美元<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-preview-can-london-870594|title=Box-Office Preview: Can 'London Has Fallen' Redeem Gerard Butler After 'Gods of Egypt'?|accessdate=2016-03-04|date=2016-03-03|last=McClintock|first=Pamela|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304095505/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-preview-can-london-870594|archivedate=2016-03-04}}</ref><ref name="PPP">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/zootopia-london-has-fallen-box-office-preview-whiskey-tango-foxtrot-deadpool-1201712794/|title=Disney Unleashed: 'Zootopia' Toon Expected To Roar Past $60M – Weekend Preview|accessdate=2016-03-03|date=2016-03-02|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303095024/https://deadline.com/2016/03/zootopia-london-has-fallen-box-office-preview-whiskey-tango-foxtrot-deadpool-1201712794/|archivedate=2016-03-03}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-preview-can-london-870594|title=Box-Office Preview: Can 'London Has Fallen' Redeem Gerard Butler After 'Gods of Egypt'?|last=McClintock|first=Pamela|date=2016-03-03|newspaper=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|accessdate=2016-03-04|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304095505/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-preview-can-london-870594|archivedate=2016-03-04}}</ref>。後來，該片於2016年3月4日在北美地區共3100間[[3D電影|3D]]影院、365間[[IMAX|IMAX]]影院和325間大螢幕影院上映。<ref name="PPP" />它在上映前夕的週四預映中獲得了170萬美元的收入，這是迪士尼（不包含[[皮克斯动画工作室|皮克斯]]）動畫電影創下的新紀錄。<ref name="Zoo">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/weekend-box-office-zootopia-london-has-fallen-whiskey-tango-foxtrot-1201714373/|title='Zootopia' $70M Opening Is A Record For Original Disney Toon; 'London' Raises $22M; 'Whiskey' Trips – Friday Night B.O.|accessdate=2016-03-05|date=2016-03-04|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305000504/http://deadline.com/2016/03/weekend-box-office-zootopia-london-has-fallen-whiskey-tango-foxtrot-1201714373/|archivedate=2016-03-05}}</ref>由於來自各界良好的口碑，它在上映首日即獲得了1950萬美元的票房收入，此亦為皮克斯以外迪士尼動畫電影的創舉（打破《冰雪奇緣》的紀錄）<ref name="Zoo" />；同時，它也是三月上映的電影中首映日票房收入次高的動畫電影（僅次於《[[冰原歷險記2|冰原歷險記2]]》）。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/03/05/box-office-zootopia-could-score-75m-weekend-after-mammoth-19-5m-friday/|title=Box Office: 'Zootopia' Could Score $75M Weekend After Mammoth $19.5M Friday|accessdate=2016-03-06|date=2016-03-05|last=Mendelson|first=Scott|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308061440/http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/03/05/box-office-zootopia-could-score-75m-weekend-after-mammoth-19-5m-friday/|archivedate=2016-03-08}}</ref>電影上映首個週末的票房表現較預期來得更佳，共獲得了約7510萬美元的收入；這打破了《冰雪奇緣》和《大英雄天團》的紀錄，也成為三月上映的電影中首映週末票房收入最高的動畫電影（打破《[[羅雷斯|羅雷司]]》的紀錄）。<ref name=":3"/><ref name="OOO">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/weekend-box-office-zootopia-london-has-fallen-whiskey-tango-foxtrot-1201714373/|title='Zootopia' $75.1M Opening Is A Record For Original Disney Toon; Pushes 2016 Past $2 Billion Mark – Monday B.O.|accessdate=2016-03-08|date=2016-03-07|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305000504/http://deadline.com/2016/03/weekend-box-office-zootopia-london-has-fallen-whiskey-tango-foxtrot-1201714373/|archivedate=2016-03-05}}</ref><ref name="BOOM">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4164&p=.htm|title='Zootopia' Scores Disney Animation's Largest Opening Ever|accessdate=2016-03-07|date=2016-03-06|last=Brevet|first=Brad|work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|publisher=[[IMDb|IMDb]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307042430/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4164&p=.htm|archivedate=2016-03-07}}</ref>此外，其首映週末票房收入在所有原創電影中排名第四，僅次於《[[寵物當家_(電影)|寵物當家]]》、《[[腦筋急轉彎_(電影)|腦筋急轉彎]]》及《阿凡達》。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/03/06/weekend-box-office-zootopia-nabs-record-breaking-73m-debut-and-a-232m-worldwide-total/|title=Weekend Box Office: 'Zootopia' Nabs Record-Breaking $73M US Debut For $232M Worldwide Total|accessdate=2016-03-07|date=2016-03-06|last=Mendelson|first=Scott|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309172418/http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/03/06/weekend-box-office-zootopia-nabs-record-breaking-73m-debut-and-a-232m-worldwide-total/|archivedate=2016-03-09}}</ref>它在IMAX電影院中的表現也極為出色，共獲得了520萬美元的票房收入；這個成績在IMAX動畫電影中僅次於《[[玩具總動員3|玩具總動員3]]》的840萬美元。<ref name="BOOM" />

電影上映後第二個週末的票房收入達5130萬美元，較首週少了31.6%；其下降的趨勢較《[[無敵破壞王|無敵破壞王]]》緩（32.7%），但比《[[樂高玩電影|樂高玩電影]]》來得快（27%）。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/03/13/weekend-box-office-zootopia-snags-50m-deadpool-topping-700m-worldwide-star-wars-tops-930m/|title=Weekend Box Office: 'Zootopia' Snags $50M, 'Deadpool Tops $700M Global, 'Star Wars' Crosses $930M|accessdate=2016-03-14|author=Scott Mendelson|date=2016-03-13|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160314214444/http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/03/13/weekend-box-office-zootopia-snags-50m-deadpool-topping-700m-worldwide-star-wars-tops-930m/|archivedate=2016-03-14}}</ref>直到上映後的第三個週末，《動物方城市》仍是北美地區的票房冠軍，且獲得了3720萬美元的收入，較第二個週末少了28%<ref name=":4">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/allegiant-beat-by-zootopia-weekend-box-office-miracles-from-heaven-1201723263/|title='Allegiant' Gang Mauled By 'Zootopia' Animals As 'Miracles' Happen – Sunday Update|accessdate=2016-03-20|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|date=2016-03-20|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160321190503/http://deadline.com/2016/03/allegiant-beat-by-zootopia-weekend-box-office-miracles-from-heaven-1201723263/|archivedate=2016-03-21}}</ref>；這個成績在上映首週票房未達1億美元的電影中位居第二名（僅次於《阿凡達》的6800萬美元，並超越了《[[007：空降危機|007：空降危機]]》的3500萬美元）。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/03/20/weekend-box-office-star-wars-dips-under-1m-deadpool-tops-spider-man-3-zootopia-near-600m/#1e3097ea5a41|title=Weekend Box Office: 'Star Wars' Dips Under $1M, 'Deadpool' Tops 'Spider-Man 3, 'Zootopia' Near $600M|accessdate=2016-03-20|author=Scott Mendelson|date=2016-03-20|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160320225531/http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/03/20/weekend-box-office-star-wars-dips-under-1m-deadpool-tops-spider-man-3-zootopia-near-600m/#1e3097ea5a41|archivedate=2016-03-20}}</ref>此外，電影的總票房收入也在第三週突破了2億美元。<ref name=":4" />《動物方城市》在其上映後的第四週才被《[[蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光|蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光]]》超越，票房收入在北美地區屈居第二。<ref name="OP">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/batman-v-superman-opening-weekend-box-office-records-1201726300/|title='Batman V Superman' Opening Taking Pre-Summer, Easter & March & Warner Bros. Records — Early Sunday B.O. Update|accessdate=2016-03-27|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|date=2016-03-27|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160326234553/http://deadline.com/2016/03/batman-v-superman-opening-weekend-box-office-records-1201726300/|archivedate=2016-03-26}}</ref>最後，它在票房排行榜前十名中共維持了13週，略遜於《阿凡達》的14週及《冰雪奇緣》的16週。<ref name="Leggy" />

==== 其它地區 ====
[[華特迪士尼工作室電影|華特迪士尼工作室電影]]為了配合各個市場中學校的假期，《動物方城市》在世界各地上映的時間不一。它最先於2016年2月的第二週在[[比利時|比利時]]、[[丹麥|丹麥]]和[[西班牙|西班牙]]等三個地區登上大螢幕，並獲得了約480萬美元的票房收入。<ref name="Overseas7thOpening">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/02/deadpool-zoolander-2-how-to-be-single-opening-international-box-office-1201702508/|title='Deadpool,' 'Zoolander 2,' 'How To Be Single' All Jump Higher – Int'l Box Office Final|accessdate=2016-02-17|date=2016-02-16|last=Busch|first=Anita|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160216190729/http://deadline.com/2016/02/deadpool-zoolander-2-how-to-be-single-opening-international-box-office-1201702508/|archivedate=2016-02-16}}</ref>在2月的第三週，其上映地區擴展至22個市場（約佔其國際市場總數的36%），並增加了3120萬美元的收入<ref name="Overseas8thOpening">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/02/deadpool-zootopia-mermaid-hail-caesar-international-box-office-overseas-weekend-results-1201706617/|title='Deadpool' Scores $85.3M In 2nd Offshore Frame; Nears $500M Global – Intl Box Office|accessdate=2016-02-22|date=2016-02-21|last=Tartaglione|first=Nancy|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160222090229/http://deadline.com/2016/02/deadpool-zootopia-mermaid-hail-caesar-international-box-office-overseas-weekend-results-1201706617/|archivedate=2016-02-22}}</ref>；接著，電影在2月的第四週雖未於新的地區上映，但仍增加了3300萬美元的收入。<ref name="Overseas9thOpening">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/02/gods-of-egypt-deadpool-zootopia-mermaid-international-box-office-overseas-weekend-resuts-1201710506/|title='Deadpool' At $609M Global; 'Gods Of Egypt' Bows To $24M, 'Zootopia' Lands $33M 3rd Frame – Int'l B.O. Final|accessdate=2016-03-01|date=2016-02-28|last=Tartaglione|first=Nancy|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160229212820/http://deadline.com/2016/02/gods-of-egypt-deadpool-zootopia-mermaid-international-box-office-overseas-weekend-resuts-1201710506/|archivedate=2016-02-29}}</ref>進入2016年3月的第一週後，電影上映地區擴展至共45個國家（包含[[北美地区|北美地區]]及[[中國大陸|中國大陸]]）並新增了6470萬美元的收入，在全球的票房排名僅次於《[[葉問3|葉問3]]》<ref name="Overseas10thOpening">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/zootopia-biggest-debut-ever-china-russia-disney-animation-llondon-has-fallen-international-box-office-1201715311/|title='Zootopia' Is Disney Animation Champ; 'Mermaid' Makes History; Best Picture 'Spotlight' Wins Big — Int'l Box Office Final|accessdate=2016-03-07|date=2016-03-06|last=Busch|first=Anita|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306221302/http://deadline.com/2016/03/zootopia-biggest-debut-ever-china-russia-disney-animation-llondon-has-fallen-international-box-office-1201715311/|archivedate=2016-03-06}}</ref>；其中，有330萬美元是來自IMAX影院的收入。<ref name="Overseas10thOpening" />由於在中國大陸上映後次週票房的表現亮眼，它終於在3月的第二週登上全球票房排行榜的冠軍；該週之內，本片在共45個地區增加了8930萬美元的票房收入，較前一週成長了約25%。<ref name="Overseas11thOpening">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/divergent-series-allegiant-zootopia-gods-of-egypt-deadpool-international-box-office-weekend-results-overseas-1201719546/|title='Allegiant' Pledges $26.7M; 'Zootopia' Hops With $83M 5th Frame – Intl B.O. Update|accessdate=2016-03-14|author=Nancy Tartaglione|date=2016-03-13|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160314103305/https://deadline.com/2016/03/divergent-series-allegiant-zootopia-gods-of-egypt-deadpool-international-box-office-weekend-results-overseas-1201719546/|archivedate=2016-03-14}}</ref>接下來的數日，《動物方城市》皆維持全球總票房冠軍<ref name="Overseas13thOpening">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/zootopia-allegiant-divergent-revenant-kung-fu-panda-international-box-office-weekend-resultsinternational-box-office-1201723288/|title='Zootopia' A Flash Away From $600M WW; China Welcomes 'The Revenant' With $31M Bow – Intl B.O. Final|accessdate=2016-03-21|author=Nancy Tartaglione|date=2016-03-21|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322093328/http://deadline.com/2016/03/zootopia-allegiant-divergent-revenant-kung-fu-panda-international-box-office-weekend-resultsinternational-box-office-1201723288/|archivedate=2016-03-22}}</ref>，直到兩週之後才被《蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光》超越。<ref name="Overseas14thOpening">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/batman-v-superman-dawn-of-justice-zootopia-greek-wedding-revenant-international-box-office-results-1201726990/|title='Zootopia' Nears $700M Global; 'The Revenant' Crosses $500M Globally – International Box Office Final|accessdate=2016-03-29|author=Nancy Tartaglione|date=2016-03-28|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160328173508/http://deadline.com/2016/03/batman-v-superman-dawn-of-justice-zootopia-greek-wedding-revenant-international-box-office-results-1201726990/|archivedate=2016-03-28}}</ref>它的全球票房總額則在首映後的第八週突破了5億美元的關卡。<ref name="Overseas15thOpening">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/04/batman-v-superman-dawn-of-justice-zootopia-big-fat-greek-wedding-weekend-results-international-box-office-1201731145/|title='Batman V Superman' At $422.5M Offshore; 'Zootopia' Crosses $500M; 'Deadpool' Tops $750M WW – Intl Box Office Final|accessdate=2016-04-05|author=Nancy Tartaglione|date=2016-04-04|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160405031546/http://deadline.com/2016/04/batman-v-superman-dawn-of-justice-zootopia-big-fat-greek-wedding-weekend-results-international-box-office-1201731145/|archivedate=2016-04-05}}</ref>

此外，《動物方城市》在各地的首映日於西班牙（310萬美元）、比利時及丹麥（170萬美元）、[[法國|法國]]（870萬美元）、[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]（790萬美元）、[[德國|德國]]（680萬美元）、[[波蘭|波蘭]]（120萬美元）、[[印度|印度]][[英國|英國]][[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]]三国（730萬美元）、[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]（460萬美元）、[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]]（360萬美元）、[[巴西|巴西]]（260萬美元）、[[義大利|義大利]]（330萬美元）等地區都屢獲佳績<ref name="Overseas8thOpening" /><ref name="Overseas13thOpening" /><ref name="Overseas14thOpening" /><ref name="Overseas15thOpening" />；它在比利時更成為了迪士尼及皮克斯的作品中首週票房收入最高的動畫電影。<ref name="Overseas7thOpening" />{{Asof|2016|6|29|df=US}}，本片在北美以外各國家和地區的票房排名依次為中國大陸、俄羅斯、法國和德國<ref name="Overseas14thOpening" /><ref name="Overseas15thOpening" />；其中，中國大陸是本片在北美以外最大的市場，同時也是迪士尼在該市場票房收入次高的電影，僅次於《[[復仇者聯盟2：奧創紀元|復仇者聯盟2：奧創紀元]]》。<ref name="RRSS">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/zootopia-crossing-300m-globally-100m-domestic-200m-international-1201718635/|title='Zootopia' Crossing $300M Globally Today For Disney Animation|accessdate=2016-03-12|date=2016-03-11|last=Busch|first=Anita|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160312091628/https://deadline.com/2016/03/zootopia-crossing-300m-globally-100m-domestic-200m-international-1201718635/|archivedate=2016-03-12}}</ref>

中國大陸方面，《動物方城市》於2016年3月4日與北美地區同步上映。本片最初在中國大陸上映時，因同檔期電影《[[葉問3|葉問3]]》的強勢競爭，首日票房收入約2200萬元人民幣，僅為《葉問3》首日票房（1.4億元人民幣）的約七分之一，首週僅收穫1.5億元人民幣。但由於《瘋狂動物城》在當地獲得了極為優秀的口碑，吸引許多影迷前往觀看，再加上《葉問3》被質疑可能涉及假票房事件發酵的影響，本片在3月8日超越《葉問3》，成為中國大陸單日票房冠軍，並維持了約兩個星期。<ref>{{zh-hans}}{{cite news|url=http://weibo.com/2304129841/DllBKzSMm?from=page_1002062304129841_profile&wvr=6&mod=weibotime&type=comment#_rnd1458977523479|title=《中國電影報》2016第10周（2.29-3.6）票房統計|date=2016-03-08|publisher=中國電影報|accessdate=2016-03-26|archive-date=2020-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200428044402/https://www.weibo.com/2304129841/DllBKzSMm?from=page_1002062304129841_profile&wvr=6&mod=weibotime&type=comment#_rnd1458977523479|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{zh-hans}}{{cite news|url=http://ent.qq.com/a/20160308/071603.htm|title=《瘋狂動物城》逆襲成功 成今日票房冠軍|author=yiiren|date=2016-03-08|publisher=[[騰訊娛樂|騰訊娛樂]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414080342/http://ent.qq.com/a/20160308/071603.htm|archivedate=2016-04-14|accessdate=2016-03-26}}</ref>在口碑效應的影響下，《瘋狂動物城》在上映後第9日當天的單日票房達1.656億元人民幣，打破《[[功夫熊貓3|功夫熊貓3]]》於同年1月創下的中國大陸單日動畫電影票房紀錄（1.27億元人民幣），上座率達到極高的48.7%。<ref>{{zh-hans}}{{cite news|url=http://ent.163.com/16/0314/09/BI41M2GG00032DGD.html|title=「票房」《瘋狂動物城》留下的不只是票房紀錄而已|author=陈志亮|date=2016-03-14|publisher=[[網易|網易娛樂]]|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319055118/http://ent.163.com/16/0314/09/BI41M2GG00032DGD.html|archivedate=2016-03-19|access-date=2016-03-26}}</ref>3月13日，《瘋狂動物城》在中國大陸的總票房收入達到7.34億元人民幣，超越其主要競爭對手《葉問3》。<ref>{{zh-hans}}{{cite news|url=http://weibo.com/2304129841/Dmo6vqWYM?from=page_1002062304129841_profile&wvr=6&mod=weibotime&type=comment#_rnd1458977495400|title=《中國電影報》2016年第11周（3.7-3.13）票房統計|date=2016-03-15|publisher=中國電影報|access-date=2016-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171102063749/http://weibo.com/2304129841/Dmo6vqWYM?from=page_1002062304129841_profile&wvr=6&mod=weibotime&type=comment#_rnd1458977495400|archive-date=2017-11-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>3月19日，上映16天的《瘋狂動物城》票房達到10.37億元人民幣，超越《功夫熊貓3》（9.9億元人民幣）與《[[西遊記之大聖歸來|西遊記之大聖歸來]]》（9.6億元人民幣），成為中國大陸有史以來票房收入最高的動畫電影，也是中國大陸影史上首部營收超越10億元人民幣的動畫電影，而该记录直到2019年才被《[[哪吒之魔童降世|哪吒之魔童降世]]》以46.54亿的票房超越。<ref>{{zh-hans}}{{cite news|url=http://ent.southcn.com/8/2016-03/20/content_144364360.htm|title=《瘋狂動物城》票房破十億 成國內最賣座動畫|author=马嫚丽|date=2016-03-20|publisher=[[南方報業傳媒集團|南方網]]|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160403221124/http://ent.southcn.com/8/2016-03/20/content_144364360.htm|archivedate=2016-04-03|access-date=2016-03-26}}</ref>此外，因反響熱烈，[[中華人民共和國國家新聞出版廣電總局|國家新聞出版廣電總局]]也罕見地批准該片的放映期延長2週，使得這部電影在中國大陸共放映了44天。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/robcain/2016/03/31/disneys-zootopia-gets-2-week-extension-of-its-fabulous-china-theatrical-run/#3a05910f4af6|title=Disney's 'Zootopia' Gets Two-Week Extension Of Its Fabulous China Theatrical Run|accessdate=2016-03-31|author=Rob Cain|date=2016-03-31|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160403055020/http://www.forbes.com/sites/robcain/2016/03/31/disneys-zootopia-gets-2-week-extension-of-its-fabulous-china-theatrical-run/#3a05910f4af6|archivedate=2016-04-03}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/china-box-office-batman-v-880347|title=China Box Office: 'Batman v Superman' Sinks 78 Percent in Second Weekend, Lands in Third Place|accessdate=2016-04-04|author=Patrick Brzeski|date=2016-04-04|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160405190203/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/china-box-office-batman-v-880347|archivedate=2016-04-05}}</ref>。其最终累计票房为15.306亿元人民币。<ref>数据查自中国大陆“国家电影专项奖金办公室”（中国内地票房最权威数据统计来源）手机APP。</ref>

