== 主題解讀 ==
《動物方城市》中包含了對現實世界裡[[偏見|偏見]]、[[刻板印象|刻板印象]]、[[種族歧視|種族歧視]]等議題的隱喻<ref name=":8">{{en}}{{Cite web|url=http://fusion.net/story/275485/zootopia-police-racism-race-relations-commentary/|title=What 'Zootopia' has to say about the police, race relations, and diversity|accessdate=2016-07-02|date=2016-03-04|last=Pulliam-Moore|first=Charles|publisher={{tsl|en|Fusion (TV channel)|Fusion}}|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160624201500/http://fusion.net/story/275485/zootopia-police-racism-race-relations-commentary/|archivedate=2016-06-24}}</ref><ref name=":9">{{en}}{{Cite web|url=http://www.theroot.com/articles/culture/2016/03/zootopia_yes_disney_made_a_movie_about_racism_but_with_talking_animals/|title=Zootopia: Yes, Disney Made a Movie About White Supremacy and the War on Drugs|accessdate=2016-07-02|date=2016-03-11|last=Johnson|first=Jason|publisher={{tsl|en|The Root (magazine)|The Root}}|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160706182038/http://www.theroot.com/articles/culture/2016/03/zootopia_yes_disney_made_a_movie_about_racism_but_with_talking_animals/|archivedate=2016-07-06}}</ref><ref name=":10">{{en}}{{Cite web|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2016/03/06/zootopia-disney-s-antidote-to-donald-trump-s-racial-animus.html|title='Zootopia': Disney's Antidote to Donald Trump's Racial Animus|accessdate=2016-07-02|date=2016-03-06|last=Leon|first=Melissa|publisher=[[每日野獸|The Daily Beast]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160703031647/http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2016/03/06/zootopia-disney-s-antidote-to-donald-trump-s-racial-animus.html|archivedate=2016-07-03}}</ref><ref name=":11">{{en}}{{Cite web|url=http://moviepilot.com/posts/3833880|title=Zootopia and Racism|accessdate=2016-07-02|date=2016-03-24|last=Carlin|first=Jonathan|publisher={{tsl|en|Moviepilot|Moviepilot}}|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160710221517/http://moviepilot.com/posts/3833880|archivedate=2016-07-10}}</ref>，而媒體及影評界也對此有許多不同的解讀。<ref name="rollingstone1" /><ref name=":5" /><ref name=":7" />舉例來說，在電影中，肉食動物相較於草食動物而言是為[[少數族群|少數族群]]，就如同[[美國|美國]]社會中的[[非裔美国人|非裔]]族群。<ref name=":9" />電影劇情後半段的核心焦點為草食動物對發狂的肉食動物產生恐懼，這便影射了部分美國[[美國白人|白人]]對非裔族群的心理態度<ref name=":8" />；而反派角色楊咩咩（Dawn Bellwether）的理念則被視為[[白人優越主義|白人優越主義]]的代表。<ref name=":9" /><ref name="NewBlackMan">{{en}}{{Cite web|url=http://www.newblackmaninexile.net/2016/03/the-revolution-will-not-be-animated-not.html|title=The Revolution Will Not Be Animated: Not Quite Zootopia|accessdate=2016-07-19|author=David J. Leonard|date=2016-03-15|publisher=NewBlackMan (in Exile)|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818023508/http://www.newblackmaninexile.net/2016/03/the-revolution-will-not-be-animated-not.html|archivedate=2016-08-18}}</ref>楊咩咩試圖利用「夜嚎怪」（Night Howler）萃取液使肉食動物發狂的計畫也影射了一則未被證實的[[陰謀論|陰謀論]]<ref name="butler" /><ref name="cocaine">{{en}}{{Cite web|url=https://thedoublethumb.com/2016/03/17/zootopia-movie-about-adorable-animals-crack-cocaine/|title=Zootopia is a Movie About Adorable Animals and Crack Cocaine|accessdate=2016-07-11|date=2016-03-17|last=Ashworth|first=Boone|publisher=The Double Thumb|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816225122/https://thedoublethumb.com/2016/03/17/zootopia-movie-about-adorable-animals-crack-cocaine/|archivedate=2016-08-16}}</ref>：美國[[中央情報局|中央情報局]]曾{{tsl|en|Allegations of CIA drug trafficking|中央情報局走私毒品的指控|被指控}}於1980年代中期參與[[走私|走私]][[霹靂可卡因|霹靂可卡因]]，並在[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]的非裔社群中大量販售，導致後續非裔人士犯罪率的上升。<ref name="CIA">{{en}}{{Cite web|url=http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/pages/frontline/shows/drugs/special/cia.html|title=Cocaine, Conspiracy Theories & the C.I.A. in Central America|accessdate=2016-07-11|date=2016-03-17|last=Delaval|first=Craig|publisher=[[公共電視網_(美國)|PBS]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170427124212/http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/pages/frontline/shows/drugs/special/cia.html|archivedate=2017-04-27}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{Cite web|url=http://newsone.com/2033054/black-urban-legends-crack-black-community/|title=Conspiracy Theory 101: Crack Is Wack But Did CIA Create It To Kill Off Blacks?|accessdate=2016-07-19|date=2012-07-01|last=Manuel-Logan|first=Ruth|publisher=NEWSONE.com|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818212036/http://newsone.com/2033054/black-urban-legends-crack-black-community/|archivedate=2016-08-18}}</ref>此外，豹警官（Benjamin Clawhauser）在主角哈茱蒂至方城市警局報到時誇她「可愛」，茱蒂卻感到被冒犯；這則影射了在美國被視為禁忌的「[[黑鬼|黑鬼]]」（nigger）一詞。<ref name=":10" /><ref name=":11" />對此，導演之一的[[傑瑞·布希|傑瑞·布希]]則表示，相關的隱喻其實具有普遍性，並沒有針對一些特定的族群、種族或性別。<ref name=":6" />

許多影評對這些隱喻所帶來的效果持正面評價，如《[[每日电讯报|每日電訊報]]》的{{Tsl|en|Robbie Collin|羅比·柯林}}曾寫道：「這些有關差異性的價值的隱喻在電影中呈現得一點也不死板，而這部電影最大的優點之一，就是它深信年輕的觀眾也能夠自行解讀這則隱微、複雜的訊息。」  <ref name="Daily Telegraph 24 March 2016" />但也有評論認為這部電影在嘗試探討種族歧視、[[性別歧視主義|性別歧視]]、[[警察暴力|警察暴力]]和[[厭女主義|厭女主義]]等嚴肅議題時「過於說教、太多粉飾、有如霧裡看花」，且對於瓦解[[美國社會|美國社會]]中的制度性壓抑（structural oppression）毫無助益。<ref>{{en}}{{Cite web|url=http://watercoolerconvos.com/2016/03/15/zootopia-disneys-feeble-attempt-at-discussing-racism-without-discussing-racism/|title='Zootopia': Disney's Feeble Attempt At Discussing Racism Without Discussing Racism|accessdate=2016-07-23|author=Jenn M. Jackson|date=2016-03-15|work=WaterCoolerConvos|publisher=|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160726141559/http://watercoolerconvos.com/2016/03/15/zootopia-disneys-feeble-attempt-at-discussing-racism-without-discussing-racism/|archivedate=2016-07-26}}</ref>

