2020年12月10日，[[華特迪士尼動畫工作室|華特迪士尼動畫工作室]]在迪士尼投資者大會的直播上宣布，改編自本片的動畫劇集《[[動物方城市+|動物方城市+]]》將於2022年初在[[Disney+|Disney+]]上首映；並且會是工作室的首個電視項目之一，因為大多數基於迪士尼動畫電影的電視節目都是由[[迪士尼电视动画公司|迪士尼电视动画公司]]製作的。<ref>{{Cite web|title=‘Baymax!’, ‘Tiana’, ‘Moana & ‘Zootopia+’ Series Set For Disney+|url=https://deadline.com/2020/12/baymax-tiana-moana-zootopia-series-r-disney-plus-1234654504/|access-date=2021-05-03|date=2020-12-11|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|work=Deadline|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120115153/https://deadline.com/2020/12/baymax-tiana-moana-zootopia-series-r-disney-plus-1234654504/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=迪士尼動畫Twitter推文|url=https://twitter.com/disneyanimation/status/1337190903660756994|access-date=2021-05-03|work=Twitter|language=zh|archive-date=2021-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210530210548/https://twitter.com/DisneyAnimation/status/1337190903660756994|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Moana and Tiana get their own musical Disney Plus shows|url=https://www.polygon.com/disney-plus/2020/12/10/22168776/disney-princess-shows-disney-plus-tiana-moana-baymax-zootopia|access-date=2021-05-03|date=2020-12-10|last=Radulovic|first=Petrana|work=Polygon|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211003651/https://www.polygon.com/disney-plus/2020/12/10/22168776/disney-princess-shows-disney-plus-tiana-moana-baymax-zootopia|dead-url=no}}</ref>

